%description:
TCP Eifel timestamp undo (Workstream D2 refinement, RFC 3522 / Linux
tcp_packet_delayed): a spurious RTO proven by TIMESTAMPS alone (SACK off, so
neither D-SACK undo nor F-RTO can trigger).

The client sends one 1000-byte segment with Timestamps negotiated. The tester
DELAYS the server's ACK of it (b2) by 1.2 s -- past the client's 1 s RTO -- and
deletes the duplicate ACK (b3) elicited by the resulting retransmission (that
duplicate echoes the RETRANSMISSION's TSval and would mask the proof). The RTO
fires, the undo context is captured before the ssthresh/cwnd reduction, and the
retransmission stamps retransStampTS with the current TS clock. When the
delayed original ACK finally arrives, its TSecr echoes the ORIGINAL
transmission's TSval, which is OLDER than retransStampTS: packetDelayed() holds,
mayUndo() passes without a single D-SACK, and the pre-RTO cwnd/ssthresh are
restored (undoCwndReduction).

Falsification: with timestampSupport=false (verified during development) the
same scenario keeps the post-RTO slow-start cwnd and the "Undoing spurious cwnd
reduction" line never appears -- there is no evidence usable for the undo.

%inifile: omnetpp.ini
[General]
record-vector-results = false
ned-path = .;../../../../src;../../lib

network = inet.test.moduletest.lib.TcpTestNet1

cmdenv-event-banners=false
cmdenv-express-mode=false
cmdenv-log-prefix="[%c]: "

*.testing=false
*.tcptester.script="b2 delay 1.2;b3 delete"

*.cli_app.localAddress="10.0.0.1"
*.cli_app.localPort=1000
*.cli_app.connectAddress="10.0.0.2"
*.cli_app.connectPort=2000
*.cli_app.active=true
*.cli_app.tOpen=0s
*.cli_app.tSend=0.5s
*.cli_app.sendBytes=1000B
*.cli_app.tClose=-1s
*.cli_app.sendScript=""

*.srv_app.localAddress="10.0.0.2"
*.srv_app.localPort=2000
*.srv_app.connectAddress="10.0.0.1"
*.srv_app.connectPort=1000
*.srv_app.active=false
*.srv_app.tOpen=0s
*.srv_app.tSend=-1s
*.srv_app.sendBytes=0B
*.srv_app.tClose=-1s
*.srv_app.sendScript=""

*.*_tcp.windowScalingSupport = false
*.*_tcp.sackSupport = false
*.*_tcp.timestampSupport = true
*.*_tcp.mss = 1000
*.*_tcp.tcpAlgorithmClass = "TcpReno"
*.*_tcp.delayedAcksEnabled = false
*.*_tcp.lossUndoEnabled = true
*.*_tcp.frtoEnabled = false
*.*_tcp.tlpEnabled = false
*.*_tcp.initialRto = 1s
*.*_tcp.initialWindow = "rfc6928"
*.*_tcp.advertisedWindow = 20000

include ../../lib/tcp-legacy.ini

%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%contains: stdout
Undoing spurious cwnd reduction
%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%postrun-command: grep -c "Performing retransmission" test.out > test_rexmit_count.out || true
%contains: test_rexmit_count.out
1
%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
%postrun-command: grep "undisposed object:" test.out > test_undisposed.out || true
%not-contains: test_undisposed.out
undisposed object: (
%#--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
